      "text": "पहाडको मुनि थियो\nसानो घले गाउँ।\nखोलाछेऊ चौरी ठुलो\nबस्तु चर्ने ठाउँ।"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/worldeducationnepal%40np.worlded.org%2f9b3c2d08-c5b8-436a-bad9-f8f488aa0bf1%2f%e0%a4%98%e0%a4%b2%e0%a5%87+%e0%a4%97%e0%a4%be%e0%a4%89%e0%a4%81%e0%a4%95%e0%a5%8b+%e0%a4%95%e0%a4%a5%e0%a4%be%2fAOR_pc076.png",
      "text": "वर्ष दिनमा एकचोटि\nसबै भेला हुन्थे।\nदौडमा जित्नेलाई\nत्यहाँ राजा चुन्थे।"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/worldeducationnepal%40np.worlded.org%2f9b3c2d08-c5b8-436a-bad9-f8f488aa0bf1%2f%e0%a4%98%e0%a4%b2%e0%a5%87+%e0%a4%97%e0%a4%be%e0%a4%89%e0%a4%81%e0%a4%95%e0%a5%8b+%e0%a4%95%e0%a4%a5%e0%a4%be%2fAOR_6W-U1.png",
      "text": "बालबच्‍चा ठिटाठिटी\nथिए नरनारी।\nदौडिने चाहिँ उभेकाथे\nचिल्‍ला गोडा पारी।"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/worldeducationnepal%40np.worlded.org%2f9b3c2d08-c5b8-436a-bad9-f8f488aa0bf1%2f%e0%a4%98%e0%a4%b2%e0%a5%87+%e0%a4%97%e0%a4%be%e0%a4%89%e0%a4%81%e0%a4%95%e0%a5%8b+%e0%a4%95%e0%a4%a5%e0%a4%be%2fgroup.png",
      "text": "ठुलो भीड जम्मा भयो\nलिगलिगको कोटमा।\nठुलो घण्टी झुण्डिएको\nथियो खरी बोटमा।"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/worldeducationnepal%40np.worlded.org%2f9b3c2d08-c5b8-436a-bad9-f8f488aa0bf1%2f%e0%a4%98%e0%a4%b2%e0%a5%87+%e0%a4%97%e0%a4%be%e0%a4%89%e0%a4%81%e0%a4%95%e0%a5%8b+%e0%a4%95%e0%a4%a5%e0%a4%be%2fAOR_CMB0281.png",
      "text": "अनौठो थियो त्यो गाउँको\nरीत परम्परा।\nगर्नुपर्थ्यो जित्नलाई\nमेहनत कडा।"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/worldeducationnepal%40np.worlded.org%2f9b3c2d08-c5b8-436a-bad9-f8f488aa0bf1%2f%e0%a4%98%e0%a4%b2%e0%a5%87+%e0%a4%97%e0%a4%be%e0%a4%89%e0%a4%81%e0%a4%95%e0%a5%8b+%e0%a4%95%e0%a4%a5%e0%a4%be%2fAOR_E-1-182.png",
      "text": "त्यहीँ थियो दशैं तिहार\nत्यहीँ चाड ठुलो।\nदौड सुरू भएपछि\nउड्थ्यो भुँइको धुलो।"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/worldeducationnepal%40np.worlded.org%2f9b3c2d08-c5b8-436a-bad9-f8f488aa0bf1%2f%e0%a4%98%e0%a4%b2%e0%a5%87+%e0%a4%97%e0%a4%be%e0%a4%89%e0%a4%81%e0%a4%95%e0%a5%8b+%e0%a4%95%e0%a4%a5%e0%a4%be%2fAOR_pmt043.png",
      "text": "हाँसो ठट्टा रमाइलो\nड्याङ्ड्याङ् बज्थ्यो बाजा।\nको हुने हो? को हुने हो?\nयसपालीको राजा।"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/worldeducationnepal%40np.worlded.org%2f9b3c2d08-c5b8-436a-bad9-f8f488aa0bf1%2f%e0%a4%98%e0%a4%b2%e0%a5%87+%e0%a4%97%e0%a4%be%e0%a4%89%e0%a4%81%e0%a4%95%e0%a5%8b+%e0%a4%95%e0%a4%a5%e0%a4%be%2fAOR_CMB0280.png",
      "text": "हुल बीच थिए एक\nगोरखाली ठिटो।\nयसपालीको दौड उनले\nपुरा गरे छिटो।"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/worldeducationnepal%40np.worlded.org%2f9b3c2d08-c5b8-436a-bad9-f8f488aa0bf1%2f%e0%a4%98%e0%a4%b2%e0%a5%87+%e0%a4%97%e0%a4%be%e0%a4%89%e0%a4%81%e0%a4%95%e0%a5%8b+%e0%a4%95%e0%a4%a5%e0%a4%be%2fimage2.jpg",
      "text": "कस्ले जित्यो भन्ने ठुलो\nथियो सबको चाह।\nदौड जिती राजा भए\nत्यहाँ द्रव्य शाह।"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "img": "https://s3.amazonaws.com/BloomLibraryBooks/worldeducationnepal%40np.worlded.org%2f9b3c2d08-c5b8-436a-bad9-f8f488aa0bf1%2f%e0%a4%98%e0%a4%b2%e0%a5%87+%e0%a4%97%e0%a4%be%e0%a4%89%e0%a4%81%e0%a4%95%e0%a5%8b+%e0%a4%95%e0%a4%a5%e0%a4%be%2fimage311.png",
      "text": "अभिषेक भयो उनका\nनयाँ राजा भए।\nनाच्दै गाउँदै रमाउँदै\nदरबारमा गए।"
    }
